        "modified": "2021-10-21T05:37:24",
        "modified_gmt": "2021-10-21T05:37:24",
        "slug": "7-reasons-why-you-need-to-use-video-content-marketing",
        "status": "publish",
        "type": "post",
        "link": "https://luhaifdigitech.com/blog/2021/10/21/7-reasons-why-you-need-to-use-video-content-marketing/",
        "title": {
            "rendered": "7 Reasons Why You Need to Use Video Content Marketing"
        },
        "content": {
            "rendered": "<p>In the present time, a business that does not make use of video marketing is the same as an adolescent without a smartphone. Blogs, social media, video streaming services, and websites are significant for video marketing and enable you to reach out to your prospective clients.</p>\n<p>Video content marketing is when brands create video content to boost their profile online. Video is generally published on either YouTube or a social network, even it can also come in the shape of webinars, courses, live video, or self-hosted video. The best thing about Video marketing is that it can be a prominent way for a brand to spread its message in a way that is easily reachable to an outsized audience.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong class = \"mb-3\">Let’s take a look at the reasons why you should use video marketing in your marketing strategy:</strong><br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong class = \" mt-2 mb-3\">1.VIDEOS ARE A GREAT WAY TO EXPLAIN YOUR PRODUCT: </strong></p>\n<p>Video content is a useful tool when it comes to helping potential buyers to learn about a product. Using video content will help users to extend their understanding of a product or service. Customers will only buy your product once they understand what it does and how it will help them. It is unsurprising that video content is such a prominent tool for this because the visual element helps businesses clearly explain how things work.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong class = \"mb-3\">2.VIDEOS ARE GREAT FOR SEO: </strong></p>\n<p>Uploading videos on YouTube that focus on a common search term can be a good way to get your business on the primary page of Google. That is why Google includes YouTube videos at the top of the page for several search terms. </p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong class = \"mb-3\">3.VIDEOS ARE HELPFUL IN BOOSTING SALES: </strong></p>\n<p>Using videos on the pages can raise conversion rates by up to 80%.  This is often because videos are appealing, increase the time visitors spend on a page, and can also evoke a sense of trust in customers. One of the benefits of video marketing is it helps in increasing and boosting sales and profit. Thus, it can improve your earning.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong class = \"mb-3\">4.YOU CAN USE VIDEO IN A VAREITY OF WAYS:  </strong><br />\nWhile YouTube is the obvious place to start when creating videos and social media platforms including Snapchat, Facebook, Instagram allow you to post stories. These are great because they can be super quick and cheap to create and they speak directly to your audience. Webinars are a great way to utilize video to interact directly with your potential customers. They can be used to answer specific questions customers may have about your product or to teach the audience something about your industry.</p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><strong class = \"mb-3\">5. VIDEOS CAN EASILY GO VIRAL:  </strong></p>\n<p>With videos, you have the best chance of achieving, because they are so impactful and so easy to share therefore, can spread quickly &#038; become viral. This can increase engagement on the social media platform. It is a significant tool that can transform busy, lethargic, and lazy clients into potential ones.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong class = \"mt-2 mb-3\">6. BUILD STRONGER BRAND AFFILIATION AND CONNECTION:  </strong></p>\n<p>Watching a video provides both audio and visual stimulation. Viewers are more engaged and thus naturally develop stronger affiliation and interest within the content they are consuming.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n<strong class = \"mt-2 mb-3\">7. MOBILE USERS LOVE WATCHING VIDEOS:  </strong></p>\n<p>In this digital era, almost everyone has a smartphone and an outstanding number of people love spending time on sites that have videos in them. Also, people like using the products and services whose attributes or traits have been displayed using videos. If you have to make a personal connection between the audience and the brand, display the product in a video format so that they can connect.<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;<br />\n&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"wp-image-101 alignnone\" src=\"https://luhaifdigitech.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2021/10/VM_2.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"100%\" height=\"576\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p>Video advertising is becoming more and more reasonable and widespread. Video is a great way for marketers to reach people. It is easier than ever to share information about the product to potential customers. Creative video advertising can be spread on the Internet in a matter of days, getting millions of views. And this is the whole point of the video to engage more and more customers. At Luhaif Digitech, our skilled team of multi-disciplinary experts brings creativity and excellence to every video engagement.</p>\n",
            "protected": false
        },
