        "modified": "2020-12-30T09:21:47",
        "modified_gmt": "2020-12-30T09:21:47",
        "slug": "what-does-online-marketing-mean",
        "status": "publish",
        "type": "post",
        "link": "https://luhaifdigitech.com/blog/2019/12/12/what-does-online-marketing-mean/",
        "title": {
            "rendered": "What does Online Marketing mean?"
        },
        "content": {
            "rendered": "<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Online marketing is a collection of tools and approaches used for encouraging products and services through the internet. </span><b>Online marketing</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> encompasses an extensive range of marketing components than traditional business marketing due to the additional channels and marketing procedures available on the internet.</span></p>\n<p><b>Online marketing can deliver advantages such as:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Growth in potential</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Minimized expenses</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Distinguished communications</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Superior control</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Improved customer service</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Competitive advantage</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><img loading=\"lazy\" class=\"aligncenter wp-image-75 size-large\" src=\"https://luhaifdigitech.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/OM_1-1024x576.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1024\" height=\"576\" srcset=\"https://luhaifdigitech.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/OM_1-1024x576.png 1024w, https://luhaifdigitech.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/OM_1-300x169.png 300w, https://luhaifdigitech.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/OM_1-768x432.png 768w, https://luhaifdigitech.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/OM_1-1536x864.png 1536w, https://luhaifdigitech.com/blog/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/OM_1-2048x1152.png 2048w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px\" /></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b>Online marketing</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> is also called </span><b>Internet marketing</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">, web marketing, search engine marketing (SEM) and digital marketing.</span></p>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The comprehensive online marketing spectrum diversified according to business requirements. Effective and functional online marketing programs leverage consumer data and customer relationship management (CRM) systems. Online marketing associates organizations with qualified and knowledgeable potential customers and takes business development to a much greater level than traditional marketing.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b>Online marketing</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> incorporates the internet&#8217;s innovative and technical tools, comprising design, development, sales and advertising, while concentrating on the following primary business models:</span></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">E-commerce</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Lead-based websites</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Associate marketing</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">Local search</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n<p><b>Online marketing has various advantages that includes:</b></p>\n<ul>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Low costs:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Enormous audiences are reachable at a fraction of traditional advertising budgets, authorizing businesses to generate captivating consumer ads.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Flexibility and convenience:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Consumers may research and buy products and services at their pleasure.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Analytics:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Well organized statistical results are accelerated without additional costs.</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Multiple options:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Advertising tools incorporate pay-per-click advertising, email marketing and local search integration (like Google Maps).</span></li>\n<li style=\"font-weight: 400;\"><b>Demographic targeting:</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> Consumers can be demographically targeted much more productively in an online rather than an offline procedure.</span></li>\n</ul>\n<p><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\">The main hindrance of online marketing is the lack of manifestation, which signifies that consumers are incompetent to try out, or try on items they might wish to purchase. Beneficent return policies are the essential way to overcome such buyer apprehension.</span></p>\n<p><b>Online marketing</b><span style=\"font-weight: 400;\"> has outsold traditional advertising in recent years and extends to be a flourishing industry.</span></p>\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\n",
            "protected": false
        },
        "excerpt": {
            "rendered": "<p>Online marketing is a collection of tools and approaches used for encouraging products and services through the internet. Online marketing encompasses an extensive range of marketing components than traditional business marketing due to the additional channels and marketing procedures available on the internet. Online marketing can deliver advantages such as: Growth in potential Minimized expenses [&hellip;]</p>\n",
            "protected": false
        },
